  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9 \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d91\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0ddc\u0d9f\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Koha's eggs are eaten by caterpillars",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "We are the ones who keep Koha's eggs. The chief organizer of the ruling party, Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga, Minister of Urban Development and Housing, said in Parliament today (2) that the eggs that come to eat those eggs will be cut off.",
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga said this while commenting on the interim budget debate.",
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga said this in reply to the statement made by Samagi Jana Balavega Colombo District Councilor Dr. Harsha De Silva on the last 31st when starting the budget debate, \"Ranil's economic policy is like a chick in a nest\".",
        "\"The President invited them to forget all that and think about the country and get the country out of the crisis. The opposition compares him to someone who has laid eggs in the crow's nest. Remember that he is the first to tell us that the flowers will bloom and the years will come. Yes, we should lay our eggs there. Our nest was given. We gave it willingly. We were told where it was. Therefore, we are not going to cut it anywhere.",
        "He first tried to make drugs with you. Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga said that it was you who chased him away."
      ],
